title: Magpul Dynamics- The Art of the Tactical Carbine
description:
Magpul Dynamics: The Art of the Tactical Carbine (DVD Rips)

Full credit goes to intR452 of Demonoid for providing this, I simply moved it here to TPB...

"The Art of the Tactical Carbine is a 3-disc DVD set featuring over four hours of actual live fire class instruction and additional instructional material. With extensive combat experience around the globe, instructors Travis Haley and Chris Costa cover not only the "how to" aspects of the Carbine but also the "mindset" required to employ a carbine effectively under stress."
